{"lemma":"بِطْنَةُ","slug":"بِطْنَةُ","root":"ب.ط.ن","root_slug":"ب-ط-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ط-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n2800","n2810"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%90%D8%B7%D9%92%D9%86%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"gluttony, overeating"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/bitˤ.na/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n2800","headword_ar":"بطّنهُ","root":"bTn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taboTiynN","text_ar":"تَبْطِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 1. ―         -b2-  See also 4. ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biTaAnap","text_ar":"بِطَانَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lining, to it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a garment, or piece of cloth; (S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AbTnhu","text_ar":"ابطنهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bT~n liHayatahu","text_ar":"بطّن لِحَيَتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cut off, from that part of his beard which was beneath the chin and lower jaw."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, Nh, TA.) Accord. to the copies of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taboTiynu","text_ar":"تَبْطِينُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"All~iHoyapi","text_ar":"اللِّحْيَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not"},{"kind":"text","text":"doing so: but this is wrong. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n2810","headword_ar":"بِطْنَةٌ","root":"bTn","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Repletion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state of being much filled with food"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and drink."},{"kind":"text","text":"(So in a copy of the S.) It is said in a prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbiTonapu tu*ohibu AlfiTonapa","text_ar":"البِطْنَةُ تُذْهِبُ الفِطْنَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Repletion banishes intelligence"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  And [hence,] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Exultation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"great or excessive exultation, and insolent and unthankful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ungrateful, behaviour."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b3-  [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAta fulaAnN","text_ar":"مَاتَ فُلَانٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bibiTonatihi","text_ar":"بِبِطْنَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one died with his wealth complete, not having expended,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dispensed, anything thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, accord. to A'Obeyd, this prov. relates to religion, and means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he went forth from the present world in a state of integrity, without any infringement of his religion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tagaDogaDa","text_ar":"تَغَضْغَضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places.] [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naz~ato bihi","text_ar":"نَزَّتْ بِهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbaTinapu","text_ar":"البَطِنَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Richness caused him to exult,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exult greatly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excessively, and to behave insolently and unthankfully,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ungratefully."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}